    "Gautier covered nearly all the Salons for <em>La Presse</em> during Louis-Philippe's reign, 1830-1848.": [],
    "He wrote on architecture and the applied arts as well.": [],
    "Gautier promoted the work of Ingres and Delacroix largely through his technique of actively and personally entering into the picture's story.": [],
    "Gautier's 1843 travelogue, <em>Tra los montes</em>, and reissued as <em>Voyage en Espagne</em> in 1845, introduced France to the work of Francesco Goya.": [],
